PrecisAppointment of PETER HARRISON, of Ottawa, Ontario, as Associate Deputy Minister of Human Resources Development, to hold office during pleasure; and appointment of PETER HARRISON as commissioner of the Canada Employment Insurance Commission, who shall be the Vice-Chairperson of the Commission.
